caption.text:
Mungkin kisah cinta yang kau alami tak harus didahului dengan tertinggalnya sepatu kaca di istana,
Tak harus kau tunggangi kuda putih hingga ke ujung kota agar kau temui sang empunya sepatu kaca,
Tak harus kau tukar suaramu dengan sepasang kaki,
Tak harus kau curi selendang bidadari,
Tak harus kau gosok lampu agar kau punya 3 permintaan yang salah satu permintaanmu adalah dia,
Tak harus kau minta bunga mawar pada ayahmu hingga bertemu raksasa buruk rupa,
Tak harus juga ibu tirimu membuang dirimu di hutan hingga bertemu 7 kurcaci.
Memang kisah cintamu tak seperti dongeng yang kau ceritakan hingga seluruh dunia tahu.
Namun yang kuketahui adalah kisah cinta sederhana dengan ikatan janji setia yang kau pegang teguh selama 20 tahun.
Memang perjalanannya tak mudah, ku saksikan sendiri. 
Suka dan duka kau alami bersama, tanpa keraguan kau jalani hari-hari bahagia bersama. 
Memang tak pernah kau tunjukkan romansa percintaanmu di depanku, tapi hati dan perasaanmu tak bisa bohong, kau sayang padanya.
Senyum dan tawa bahagia serta tetesan air mata semua ku saksikan sendiri, menjadi bukti cinta kau dan dia.
Selalu menggenggam tapi tak pernah melepas.
Meski berat, namun tak pernah kau berhenti berjuang demi cinta yang telah kau bangun lama.
Ah, memang Tuhan sungguh adil.
Tak membiarkan hasil mengkhianati usaha.
Happy 20 th Anniversary Pa, Ma.
Biar kisah cinta sederhana ini menjadi panutanku menulis indah cerita cintaku agar kelak ku katakan pada dunia bahwa indahnya kisahku berdasar pada satu realita kisah cinta sederhanamu.
.
.
.
Peluk hangat,
Putri sulungmu ‚ù§

Ajari aku tentang cinta yang sederhana.
Sesederhana tak membuatnya terluka saat tak bisa tertawa bersama.
Menerima dengan lapang dada walau kekurangan seluas samudera.

Ajari aku cinta yang tulus.
Setulus apa adanya kamu bukan ada apanya kamu.
Merengkuh angin walau penuh debu. 
Ajari aku cinta yang setia. 
Setia dikala suka maupun duka. 
Tetap bergandeng tangan meski jiwa raga penuh luka.

Aku percaya ketika dua insan di pertemukan oleh Yang Kuasa atas nama cinta, maka setajamnya pisau, setingginya gunung, seluruh semestapun tak mampu memisahkan. 
Takdir Tuhan begitu indah sehingga rancangan-Nya mampu menghadirkan kau, dia, dan aku yang ku sebut kita menjadi sebuah keluarga, lagi-lagi atas nama cinta. 
Maafkan aku tak pernah mampu membuat keluarga kita bahagia dengan cara yang mungkin telah kalian impikan.
Maafkan aku yang terkadang salah, lebih mengagungkan cinta yang kutemui dalam perjalananku lebih dari cinta sederhana yang kau berikan. 
Terimakasih telah membangun sebuah rumah sederhana berhiaskan cinta yang menjadi tempatku pulang ketika putus asaku, lelah jiwaku, dan hampa anganku.

Aku bahagia :)

"Every hello, ends with a goodbye"
Never regret everything that happened in my life.
God is the best writer ever that write each chapter of my life for the best, even before I knew what life is.
God never do something without a purpose and so does our meeting.
I still remember our first chat and that was amazing to find someone who had the same thought :)
I still remember our first fight before our first meeting and that was too sad to be remembered. You did everything to make me talk to you and that was amazing.
I remember our first skype and you got nothing to wear and you were too shy and I couldnt speak just laughed slowly cause I didnt want to disturb the others cause it's late and that was amazing. 
I remember our first meeting, when you came there even when you had nothing to do there and that was amazing.
I remember our first date after that huge fight and that was a long night, but you said you love me and that was amazing.
I remember our first mansiv and that doll and all the hugs and kisses that was super amazing.
Those smiles, laughs, silly jokes, hugs, kisses, foods, fights, tears, presents, times, calls, spirits, words and prayers are the most amazing thing I've ever had and I thank God the most cause you never fail to amaze me even once and I don't know why.
Even sometimes we hurt each other, you never fail to impress me.
But time flies so fast and you aren't even mine now. It's hard to face the truth and accept the rejection.
I can't deny my feelings to you and so are you.
I know you are tired and for some reason giving up on me, but I've tried my best.
I can't force you to love me cause I know it has changed, it's not the same.
But I want you to know that you always have that place. And when you are tired and have nobody to lean on, I always be your home :)
Our goodbye was the most thing that amazingly ruined my life and I do remember it. When you said your love had change and even it's not there anymore.
But if I could change one of those memories, I'll choose the last part, the "goodbye" part, and turn it back to the first part when you say "hello" for the first time and smile for the first time like "goodbye" will never happen :)

caption.text:
Being your daughter for 17 years is a bliss. God is loving me that much so He gave you to me with a lot of purposes. God chose you because you are the strongest and the most patient that can handle me.
To be a mother of me, I know it's so hard. But I never hear you complaining about me. We often fight and argue, we may not like each other sometimes, but it doesnt matter.
In a problem, you are my solution. In a garden of heart, you are the only flower that blooms while the others die. In seasons, you are my summer and winter. Extremely hot and cold yet it's my favorite. In colours, you are pink because you are soft and bright.
You are my sun and my moon. My morning and my night.
Once, I asked you about your ideal child, but you said that it doesnt matter. There's no perfect child nor mom, they just completing each other. So do us. And you just perfect and incredible. Never leave me. Always be there on my best or my worst.
Thankyou for giving me a beautiful life.
Thankyou for your lips, decorating my life with the colours of your emotions.
Thankyou for your hands, taking care of me and wiping my tears.
Thankyou for your eyes, warming my day like a sunshine.
Thankyou for your ears, hearing all the stories and grumbles
Thankyou for your feet, picking me up no matter where I am.
Thankyou for your heart, loving me sincerely.
Thankyou for your advices, guiding my steps.
Thankyou for never giving up on me.
Thankyou for your forgiveness, forgiving all my faults, even Im not saying sorry.
Im sorry for ruining the whole life of yours, Im sorry for making you ashame, Im sorry for hurting you everday, every hours, every minutes, and every seconds in your life, Im sorry for making you tired and exhausted, bored and dissapointed, angry, mad, furious, crazy and sick. Im sorry for each tears that you dropped for me. Im sorry.
I know you deserve a child better than me, yet you still believe that Im perfect.
Thankyou.

Happy 40th birthday Mama, I love you so much.
Wishing you a long life.
Stay strong.
Stay awesome.
Please stay with me forever.
I want you to be the first that feel the joy of my success, just like the first that saw me on earth, heard my cry, and looked my smile.

Every valentine was only about receiving.
I never shared the happiness I got every year cause I thought it's useless.
Time flies, people change, feeling change, so do I.

I know that this was spoken by a lot of people before, but it's true.
Love is all about sharing. 
And I want to share my love with this chocolates as the symbols. 
I got no chocolates today nor flowers nor love letters.
But your cute smile colours my day.
Your surprised face made my day.
And your hug warmed my day.
What a special day.
Thanks for being my valentine‚ô°

Being a sister isnt that easy, especially to be yours.
When all sisters were sharing their love life on my age,
Im sharing a craziness and hapiness in my own way,
With some tears and angers.
Show you how to face the world with smile and laughter,
While encouraging you to keep strong,
And if you cant fight them any longer, you can hold me tight.
I'll give you more than what you ask.
If you ask me a hug, i'll give you a warm embrace
If you ask me an advice, 
I'll give you a hand to walk together.
I know that Im not a perfect sister you asked to God before you were born,
But I could make you sure of me that you can relay on me everytime you need.
And look at us know, we're laughing the same language !
I couldnt promise you a perfect happiness, 
But I could promise you a perfect love inside the imperfectness.
Forgive me and excuse me for all my flaws.
And belive me, I'm trying my best to protect you and our lil brother, giving all my love and share all my happiness and lil tears.
Trying to be your sister, friend, best friend, protector, teacher, role model, and everything you need.
I'll try everthing before you so that I can tell you what will hurt you there.
But dont worry, I'll beat them for you so there's no one can even touch you.
I'll prepare you to be a fighter so one day when im not around you can protect yourself.
Ohh.. I almost forget that you're a sister too for our brother.
Just give him what I gave to you if I couldnt stand anymore, oneday.
I love you to the moon and back :")
